Resources.Source: The session is not in a state where a new activity may be selected. In Execute view, only Active sessions may navigate to a selected activity.
Resources.Translation: Seja ni v stanju, ko bi lahko izbrali novo dejavnost. V Izvršnem pogledu se lahko samo aktivne seje premaknejo na izbrano dejavnost.

Resources.Source: The current activity cannot be exited. There must be a current activity in an active session in order to exit it.
Resources.Translation: Trenutne dejavnosti ne morete zaključiti. V aktivni seji mora biti trenutna dejavnost, da jo lahko zaključite.

Resources.Source: The LoggingOptions property may not be set when reviewing a session.
Resources.Translation: Lastnost LoggingOptions ne sme biti nastavljena ob pregledovanju seje.

Resources.Source: Moving to the previous activity is not valid. In Execute view, only Active sessions with a current activity may navigate to the next activity.
Resources.Translation: Premikanje na prejšnjo dejavnost ni veljavno. V Izvršnem pogledu se lahko samo aktivne seje s trenutno dejavnostjo premaknejo na naslednjo dejavnost.

Resources.Source: It is not valid to reactivate the current session. Only a completed or abandoned session may be reactivated, and only in RandomAccess view.
Resources.Translation: Ni veljavno znova aktivirati trenutne seje. Samo zaključene ali zapuščene seje je možno znova aktivirati in to v Bralno-pisalnem pogledu.

Resources.Source: The session cannot be exited in its current state. In Execute view, only Active sessions which have been started may be exited. Sessions may not be exited in other views.
Resources.Translation: Seja ne more biti zaključena v trenutnem stanju. V Izvršnem pogledu se lahko zaključijo samo aktivne seje, ki so bile zagnane. Seje ne morejo biti zaključene v drugih pogledih.

Resources.Source: The current activity cannot be abandoned. There must be a current activity in an active session in order to abandon it.
Resources.Translation: Trenutne dejavnosti ne morete opustiti. V aktivni seji mora biti trenutna dejavnost, da jo lahko opustite.

Resources.Source: An initial activity could not be identified in the session.
Resources.Translation: V seji ni možno opredeliti začetne dejavnosti.

Resources.Source: The attempt associated with this session has not ended.
Resources.Translation: Poskus povezan s to sejo se ni zaključil.

Resources.Source: The session cannot be suspended in its current state. In Execute view, only Active sessions may be suspended. Sessions may not be suspended in other views.
Resources.Translation: Seja ne more biti začasno zaustavljena v trenutnem stanju. V Izvršnem pogledu se lahko začasno zaustavijo samo aktivne seje. Seje ne morejo biti začasno zaustavljene v drugih pogledih.

Resources.Source: The session cache cannot be cleared because the current session contains an active attempt.
Resources.Translation: Predpomnilnika seje ni možno počistiti, ker trenutna seja vsebuje aktiven poskus.

Resources.Source: Navigation requests cannot be processed. In an ExecuteView, the AttemptStatus must be Active. This call is not valid in RandomAccess and Review views.
Resources.Translation: Zahtev po krmarjenju ni možno obdelati. V Izvršnem pogledu mora biti Stanje poskusa aktivno. Ta klic ni veljaven v Bralno-pisalnem in Pregledovalnem pogledu.

Resources.Source: A session may only be started on an active attempt in ExecuteView. The session may not be in Review or RandomAccess view when calling this method.
Resources.Translation: Sejo je možno zagnati samo v aktivnem poskusu v Izvršnem pogledu. Seja ne sme biti v Pregledovalnem ali Bralno-pisalnem pogledu, ko kliče to metodo.

Resources.Source: The session cannot be abandoned in its current state. In Execute view, only Active sessions may be abandoned. Sessions may not be abandoned in other views.
Resources.Translation: Seja ne more biti opuščena v trenutnem stanju. V Izvršnem pogledu se lahko opustijo samo aktivne seje. Seje ne morejo biti opuščene v drugih pogledih.

Resources.Source: The current activity in the session does not have an associated resource. The content cannot be displayed.
Resources.Translation: Trenutna dejavnost v seji nima povezanega vira. Vsebine ni možno prikazati.

Resources.Source: Moving to the next activity is not valid. In Execute view, only Active sessions with a current activity may navigate to the next activity.
Resources.Translation: Premikanje na naslednjo dejavnost ni veljavno. V Izvršnem pogledu se lahko samo aktivne seje s trenutno dejavnostjo premaknejo na naslednjo dejavnost.

Resources.Source: The content cannot be rendered. In Execute view, the session must have an AttemptStatus of Active.
Resources.Translation: Vsebine ni možno upodobiti. V Izvršnem pogledu mora seja imeti aktivno Stanje poskusa.

Resources.Source: The changes to the current session cannot be committed. The session may not be in Review view when calling this method.
Resources.Translation: Sprememb trenutne seje ni možno uveljaviti. Seja ne sme biti v Pregledovalnem pogledu, ko kliče to metodo.

Resources.Source: The attempt has already started. You may not call Start more than once.
Resources.Translation: Poskus je že zagnan. Zagona ne morete klicati več kot enkrat.

Resources.Source: The session cannot be resumed in its current state. In Execute view, only Suspended sessions may be resumed. Sessions may not be resumed in other views.
Resources.Translation: Seje ni mogoče nadaljevati v trenutnem stanju. V Izvršnem pogledu se lahko nadaljujejo samo začasno zaustavljene seje. Sej ni možno nadaljevati v drugih pogledih.

Resources.Source: The folder '{0}' must exist prior to calling this method.
Resources.Translation: Mapa '{0}' mora obstajati pred klicem te metode.

Resources.Source: The LearningStoreItemIdentifier {0} does not represent a package in LearningStore.
Resources.Translation: LearningStoreItemIdentifier {0} ne predstavlja paketa v LearningStore.

Resources.Source: Could not find a unique directory name to use for the files.
Resources.Translation: Ni mogoče najti enoličnega imena imenika za uporabo za te datoteke.

Resources.Source: The package cannot be added to the store because it contains at least one error.
Resources.Translation: Paketa ni možno dodati v shrambo, ker vsebuje vsaj eno napako.

Resources.Source: The package cannot be added to LearningStore because the manifest in the package cannot be read.
Resources.Translation: Paketa ni možno dodati v LearningStore, ker ni možno prebrati manifesta paketa.

Resources.Source: The package must contain at least one organization and one item in order to be added to LearningStore.
Resources.Translation: Paket mora vsebovati vsaj eno organizacijo in en element, da ga lahko dodate v LearningStore.

Resources.Source: This operation cannot be performed in Execute view.
Resources.Translation: Te operacije ni možno izvesti v Izvršnem pogledu.

Resources.Source: This operation cannot be performed during the auto-grading process.
Resources.Translation: Te operacije ni možno izvesti med postopkom samodejnega ocenjevanja.

Resources.Source: The requested operation cannot be performed because the session has been completed.
Resources.Translation: Zahtevane operacije ni možno izvesti, ker je bila seja dokončana.

Resources.Source: The requested operation cannot be performed because the session has been abandoned.
Resources.Translation: Zahtevane operacije ni možno izvesti, ker je bila seja opuščena.

Resources.Source: Attachment exceeds maximum size of {0} bytes.
Resources.Translation: Priloga presega največjo velikost {0} bajtov.

Resources.Source: This operation is only valid during auto-grading.
Resources.Translation: Ta operacija je veljavna samo med samodejnim ocenjevanjem.

Resources.Source: The attempt could not be accessed. You may not have access to it, the attempt may have been deleted or does not exist.
Resources.Translation: Dostop do poskusa ni možen. Morda nimate dostopa do poskusa, je bil izbrisan ali ne obstaja.

Resources.Source: This operation cannot be performed in Review view.
Resources.Translation: Te operacije ni možno izvesti v Pregledovalnem pogledu.

Resources.Source: The requested operation cannot be performed because the session is not complete.
Resources.Translation: Zahtevane operacije ni možno izvesti, ker seja ni dokončana.

Resources.Source: The root activity id could not be accessed. Either it does not exist or you do not have permission to access it.
Resources.Translation: Dostop do korenskega identifikatorja dejavnosti ni možen. Bodisi ne obstaja ali nimate dovoljenja za dostop.

Resources.Source: A current activity is required for this operation.
Resources.Translation: Za to operacijo je zahtevana trenutna dejavnost.

Resources.Source: This operation cannot be performed on a session with an AttemptStatus of Active.
Resources.Translation: Te operacije ni možno izvesti nad sejo z aktivnim Stanjem poskusa.

Resources.Source: Global Objective database contains non-unique entries.
Resources.Translation: Zbirka podatkov Global Objective vsebuje vnose, ki niso enolični.

Resources.Source: The LearnerId could not be accessed. Either it does not exist or you do not have permission to access it.
Resources.Translation: Dostop do LearnerId ni možen. Bodisi ne obstaja ali nimate dovoljenja za dostop.

Resources.Source: The requested activity cannot be found within the session.
Resources.Translation: Zahtevane dejavnosti v seji ni možno najti.

Resources.Source: Column '{0}' not found in the view.
Resources.Translation: Stolpca '{0}' ni bilo mogoče najti v pogledu.

Resources.Source: At least one value must be provided.
Resources.Translation: Podana mora biti vsaj ena vrednost.

Resources.Source: More than one value has been provided for property '{0}'.
Resources.Translation: Za lastnost '{0}' je bila podana več kot ena vrednost.

Resources.Source: Property 'Id' can not be changed.
Resources.Translation: Lastnosti 'Id' ni možno spremeniti.

Resources.Source: Invalid condition value: only item identifiers with unique keys can be compared against.
Resources.Translation: Neveljavna vrednost pogoja: primerjati je možno samo identifikatorje elementov z enoličnimi ključi.

Resources.Source: The results of the job can not be cast to the specified return value.
Resources.Translation: Rezultatov opravila ni možno pretvoriti v določeno povratno vrednost.

Resources.Source: Right '{0}' not found in the schema.
Resources.Translation: Desnega '{0}' ni bilo mogoče najti v shemi.

Resources.Source: Timeout value specified for the transaction must be zero.
Resources.Translation: Vrednost časovne omejitve za transakcijo mora biti nič.

Resources.Source: Invalid condition value: an Xml column can only be compared against null.
Resources.Translation: Neveljavna vrednost pogoja: XML stolpec je možno primerjati samo z ničelno vrednostjo.

Resources.Source: Unique key not available.
Resources.Translation: Enoličen ključ ni na voljo.

Resources.Source: Invalid condition operator: a Guid column can only be compared with an equality or inequality operator.
Resources.Translation: Neveljaven operator pogoja: stolpec GUID je lahko primerjan z operatorjema je enako ali ni enako.

Resources.Source: A transaction already exists in this scope.
Resources.Translation: V tem obsegu transakcija že obstaja.

Resources.Source: Invalid cast.
Resources.Translation: Neveljavna pretvorba.

Resources.Source: Invalid value for property '{0}': {1}
Resources.Translation: Neveljavna vrednost za lastnost '{0}': {1}

Resources.Source: The query is not compatible with this LearningStore instance.
Resources.Translation: Poizvedba ni združljiva s tem primerkom LearningStore.

Resources.Source: Item not found
Resources.Translation: Elementa ni bilo mogoče najti

Resources.Source: Property '{0}' not found
Resources.Translation: Lastnosti '{0}' ni bilo mogoče najti

Resources.Source: More than one item matches the properties in the AddOrUpdateItem command.
Resources.Translation: Več kot en element se ujema z lastnostmi v ukazu AddOrUpdateItem.

Resources.Source: Item type '{0}' not found in the schema.
Resources.Translation: Vrste elementa '{0}' ni bilo mogoče najti v shemi.

Resources.Source: Must be a Guid.
Resources.Translation: Mora biti GUID.

Resources.Source: Parameter '{0}' not found in the view.
Resources.Translation: Parametra '{0}' ni bilo mogoče najti v pogledu.

Resources.Source: The database was created by a different version of this product.
Resources.Translation: Zbirko podatkov je ustvarila drugačna različica tega izdelka.

Resources.Source: Transaction scope disposed in invalid thread.
Resources.Translation: Obseg transakcije sproščen v neveljavni niti.

Resources.Source: Isolation level specified for the transaction doesn't match the isolation level for the currently-existing transaction.
Resources.Translation: Določena raven izolacije za transakcijo se ne ujema z ravnjo izolacije za trenutno obstoječo transakcijo.

Resources.Source: The debug log has already been enabled.
Resources.Translation: Dnevniški zapiski za odpravljanje težav so že omogočeni.

Resources.Source: A sort order for the specified column already exists in the query.
Resources.Translation: Vrstni red za določen stolpec v poizvedbi že obstaja.

Resources.Source: Column '{0}' has already been added to the query
Resources.Translation: Stolpec '{0}' je bil že dodan v poizvedbo

Resources.Source: Invalid format.
Resources.Translation: Neveljavna oblika.

Resources.Source: Cannot search on XML property '{0}'.
Resources.Translation: Ni možno iskati po lastnosti XML '{0}'.

Resources.Source: Security check failed.
Resources.Translation: Varnostno preverjanje ni uspelo.

Resources.Source: Invalid parameter value: {0}
Resources.Translation: Neveljavna vrednost parametra: {0}

Resources.Source: Invalid parameter value: only item identifiers with unique keys can be used as parameters.
Resources.Translation: Neveljavna vrednost parametra: kot parametre je možno uporabiti samo identifikatorje elementov z enoličnimi ključi.

Resources.Source: Parameter '{0}' not found in the right.
Resources.Translation: Parametra '{0}' ni bilo mogoče najti na desni.

Resources.Source: At least one output column must be specified in the query.
Resources.Translation: V poizvedbi mora biti določen vsaj en izhodni stolpec.

Resources.Source: Invalid value for property '{0}'
Resources.Translation: Neveljavna vrednost za lastnost '{0}'

Resources.Source: Enum type '{0}' not found in the schema.
Resources.Translation: Vrste oštevilčenja '{0}' ni bilo mogoče najti v shemi.

Resources.Source: Invalid condition value: {0}
Resources.Translation: Neveljavna vrednost pogoja: {0}

Resources.Source: Invalid schema definition
Resources.Translation: Neveljavna definicija sheme

Resources.Source: Invalid condition operator: null can only be compared with an equality or inequality operator.
Resources.Translation: Neveljaven operator pogoja: ničelno vrednost je možno primerjati samo z operatorjema je enako ali ni enako.

Resources.Source: Object reference not set to an instance of an object when attempting to access database. Database connection may have been lost.
Resources.Translation: Sklic na predmet ni nastavljen na primerek objekta ob poskusu dostopa do zbirke podatkov. Morda je prekinjena povezava z zbirko podatkov.

Resources.Source: Invalid transaction scope nesting.
Resources.Translation: Neveljavno gnezdenje obsega transakcije.

Resources.Source: The operation failed because of a constraint violation.
Resources.Translation: Operacija ni uspela zaradi kršitve omejitve.

Resources.Source: Cannot be null.
Resources.Translation: Ne sme biti nič.

Resources.Source: Column can not be sorted on.
Resources.Translation: Stolpec ne omogoča razvrščanja.

Resources.Source: Must be a LearningStoreItemIdentifier with ItemType '{0}'.
Resources.Translation: Mora biti LearningStoreItemIdentifier z vrsto elementa '{0}'.

Resources.Source: Method has already been called.
Resources.Translation: Metoda je bila že klicana.

Resources.Source: Must be a LearningStoreXml.
Resources.Translation: Mora biti LearningStoreXml.

Resources.Source: Must be a valid value from '{0}'.
Resources.Translation: Mora biti veljavna vrednost od '{0}'.

Resources.Source: Invalid value for parameter '{0}': {1}
Resources.Translation: Neveljavna vrednost za parameter '{0}': {1}

Resources.Source: Positive value expected
Resources.Translation: Pričakovana pozitivna vrednost

Resources.Source: Value for property '{0}' not found
Resources.Translation: Vrednosti za lastnost '{0}' ni bilo mogoče najti

Resources.Source: Must be a System.Byte array.
Resources.Translation: Mora biti matrika System.Byte.

Resources.Source: Must be between SqlDateTime.MinValue and SqlDateTime.MaxValue.
Resources.Translation: Mora biti med SqlDateTime.MinValue in SqlDateTime.MaxValue.

Resources.Source: View '{0}' not found in the schema.
Resources.Translation: Pogleda '{0}' ni bilo mogoče najti v shemi.

Resources.Source: Invalid value for parameter '{0}'
Resources.Translation: Neveljavna vrednost za parameter '{0}'

Resources.Source: Overflow.
Resources.Translation: Prekoračitev.
